{"tid":1966216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際科學期刊《自然》向中國道歉： 曾將病毒與武漢掛鈎","createTime":"2020-04-10T04:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T18:23:42.000Z","uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fe38e7c77dbdbcaeffd3c2b01c7b9b8b78a8643d","tid":1966216,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:35:18.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】《自然》向中國道歉： 曾將病毒與武漢掛鈎<br />\n<br />\n世衞（WHO）總幹事譚德塞批評台灣人涉嫌種族歧視、人身攻擊，國際科學期刊《自然》（Nature）9日出版的最新一期，自我承認犯下歧視的錯誤，表示曾把病毒與武漢和中國掛鈎，對此向中國人道歉。<br />\n<br />\n《自然》發表一篇題為〈停止對新冠肺炎的污名化〉（Stop the coronavirus stigma now）的社論，文中指出，這波疫情充斥着種族歧視和各種偏見，尤其是對亞裔人的歧視，並稱教育與研究領域將為此付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n文中更指出，世衞於2月宣佈使用「COVID-19」命名病毒，並委婉地提醒曾經在新聞報道中、錯誤地將病毒與武漢和中國掛鈎的人和組織，《自然》表示，自己也曾犯下這個「錯誤」，因此願意負起責任並道歉。<br />\n<br />\n《自然》旗下的《Nature自然科研》（Nature Research），昨日透過微信公眾號發表這篇社論的簡體中文版，希望能向中國民眾精準地傳達《自然》對這場疫病的態度與稱呼。<br />\n<br />\n文中批評美國總統特朗普和巴西總統波索納洛（Jair Bolsonaro）之子，以及英國政客，因為這些國際政要，都曾經將武漢肺炎歸咎於「中國的錯」，文章批評這些人「守舊」。文章也稱，武漢肺炎被污名化的結果，造成不少亞裔人士遭到歧視。中國在海外的留學生約70萬人，雖然大部份已返國，但還有部份學生依然留在國外，他們現在左右為難，一方面害怕繼續遭受種族歧視，一方面又擔心未來學業的不確定性。<br />\n<br />\n文中指出，多年以來將病毒性疾病與疫情首先爆發的地區、地點或區域關聯在一起，例如中東呼吸綜合症（Middle East respiratory syndrome, MERS），以及寨卡病毒（以烏干達的森林命名）。但世衞在2015年發出指引，要求停止這種做法，以減少污名化和惡劣影響，減低當地民眾的恐懼或憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n文章最後總結指：「我們必須竭盡所能地避免和減少污名化，不要把COVID-19和特定的人群或地方相提並論，病毒不會歧視。」<br />\n<br />\n《自然》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200410/XDHK2H353ZYTNW4DDA67F3OVP4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200410%2FXDHK2H353ZYTNW4DDA67F3OVP4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi67Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=04f8da6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200410%2FXDHK2H353ZYTNW4DDA67F3OVP4%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=25968e7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200410/XDHK2H353ZYTNW4DDA67F3OVP4/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"dfa2858caafe113e3c5844d43c49ec473ade5e8b","tid":1966216,"uid":38293,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"日本腦炎"},{"pid":"bfad9d6430625c861f9241b48f483e188ec0c110","tid":1966216,"uid":38293,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"西班牙流感"},{"pid":"cdf031f059e6254159ee03ad4b2a422965e413e9","tid":1966216,"uid":38293,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:36:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母Nature"},{"pid":"6dceabf1ec2316ed9db7033c608bd0bdc66cbeb4","tid":1966216,"uid":117276,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"收咗幾多人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc21ce5a36ab36f70a94e111946d7524913d56c","tid":1966216,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:37:04.000Z","msg":"斯德哥爾摩症後群"},{"pid":"adf1194541e316a102b2e48591c0861bb070a420","tid":1966216,"uid":125168,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6dceabf1ec2316ed9db7033c608bd0bdc66cbeb4","tid":1966216,"uid":117276,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:36:35.000Z","msg":"收咗幾多人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AYmvatK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAYmvatK.png&h=3d7d41a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f6285e96c0e7fcbf5186a3ac210ffbb20053474","tid":1966216,"uid":309148,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T04:37